Question Title: Leap Year Checker

Question Description:

You are given a year. Write a Java program that determines whether it is a leap year or not.

The rules for determining a leap year are as follows:

Â· A year is a leap year if it is divisible by 4 and not divisible by 100, 
or if it is divisible by 400.

Write a Java program that checks if a given year is a leap year.

Sample Input 1:

2020

Sample Output 1:

2020 is a leap year.

Sample Input 2:

2021

Sample Output 2:

2021 is not a leap year.